an AG, Rall TW, Nies AS, Taylor P, eds. "Goodman and Gilman''s the Pharmacological Basis of Therapeutics. 8th ed." New York, NY: Pergamon Press Inc. (1990):[8] "Product Information. Rexulti (brexpiprazole)." Otsuka American Pharmaceuticals Inc, Rockville, MD.[9] "Product Information. Sutent (sunitinib)." Pfizer U.S. Pharmaceuticals Group, New York, NY.', 1767365208);
